      • getLastTestCasesExecuted

        @Query(value="SELECT p.totalExecutedTestCases as count from AutomationOutputModel p where p.pai.inputExcelName=:inputExcel and p.pai.inputSheetName=:inputSheet and p.pai.executionDataTime=(SELECT max(pe.pai.executionDataTime) from AutomationOutputModel pe where pe.pai.inputExcelName=:inputExcel and pe.pai.inputSheetName=:inputSheet)")
